OL,3,CLabour councillor cleared over cutting
OL,4,Cthroats comment at London rally
OL,6,FA Labour councillor who called for far-
OL,7,Fright activists' throats to be cut at
OL,8,Fan anti-racism rally in the wake of
OL,9,Fthe Southport murders has been found
OL,10,Fnot guilty of encouraging violent
OL,11,Fdisorder.
OL,13,FRicky Jones, 58, faced trial at
OL,14,FSnaresbrook Crown Court accused of the
OL,15,Foffence after he described
OL,16,Fdemonstrators as "disgusting Nazi
OL,17,Ffascists".
