OL,3,CLabour councillor cleared over cutting
OL,4,Cthroats comment at London rally
OL,6,FA video showing Jones addressing
OL,7,Fcrowds on Hoe Street in Walthamstow,
OL,8,Feast London, on August 7 last year
OL,9,Fwent viral on social media after the
OL,10,Fprotest, which had been organised in
OL,11,Fresponse to plans for a far-right
OL,12,Fmarch outside Waltham Forest
OL,13,FImmigration Bureau.
OL,15,FThe now-suspended councillor, wearing
OL,16,Fa black polo top and surrounded by
OL,17,Fcheering supporters, said: "They are
OL,18,Fdisgusting Nazi fascists. We need to
OL,19,Fcut all their throats and get rid of
OL,20,Fthem all."
