OL,6,FHe also drew his finger across his
OL,7,Fthroat as he spoke to the crowd.
OL,9,FJurors deliberated for just over half
OL,10,Fan hour and found him not guilty on
OL,11,FFriday.
OL,13,FThe 58-year-old, who at the time was
OL,14,Falso employed as a full-time official
OL,15,Ffor the Transport Salaried Staffs'
OL,16,FAssociation (TSSA) union, was arrested
OL,17,Fon August 8 last year and interviewed
OL,18,Fat Brixton police station that night.
