OL,3,CLabour councillor cleared over cutting
OL,4,Cthroats comment at London rally
OL,6,FJones, who has been a borough
OL,7,Fcouncillor in Dartford, Kent, since
OL,8,F2019, was suspended by the Labour
OL,9,FParty the day after the incident.
OL,11,FProsecutor Ben Holt previously told
OL,12,Fthe court Jones, a father of four and
OL,13,Fgrandfather, used "inflammatory,
OL,14,Frabble-rousing language in the throng
OL,15,Fof a crowd described as a tinderbox".
OL,17,FHe told jurors Jones's speech was
OL,18,Famplified through a microphone and
OL,19,Fspeakers and took place "in a setting
OL,20,Fwhere violence could readily have been
OL,21,Fanticipated".
