OL,3,CLabour councillor cleared over cutting
OL,4,Cthroats comment at London rally
OL,6,FGiving evidence in his trial, Jones
OL,7,Fsaid his comment did not refer to far-
OL,8,Fright protesters involved in the riots
OL,9,Fat the time, but to those who had
OL,10,Freportedly left National Front
OL,11,Fstickers on a train with razor blades
OL,12,Fhidden behind them.
OL,14,FBefore he made the comment, jurors
OL,15,Fwere shown video where he said to
OL,16,Fcrowds: "You've got women and children
OL,17,Fusing these trains during the summer
OL,18,Fholidays.
OL,20,F"They don't give a **** about who they
OL,21,Fhurt."
