OL,6,FHe told the court he was "appalled" by
OL,7,Fpolitical violence, adding: "I've
OL,8,Falways believed the best way to make
OL,9,Fpeople realise who you are and what
OL,10,Fyou are is to do it peacefully."
OL,12,FJones, who said he was on the left of
OL,13,Fthe Labour Party, previously told
OL,14,Fjurors the riots had made him feel
OL,15,F"upset" and "angry" and said he felt
OL,16,Fit was his "duty" to attend counter-
OL,17,Fprotests, despite being warned to stay
OL,18,Faway from such demonstrations by the
OL,19,FLabour Party.
